{"tid":1644612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"重建連儂牆！","createTime":"2019-10-10T15:22:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T17:29:53.000Z","uid":245203,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"078eb84f4e39b01d8107b94be97134000b6b2910","tid":1644612,"uid":245203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:22:04.000Z","msg":"發覺呢兩三日啲連儂牆好多都俾人拆咗<br />\n<br />\n無論係普通行人路定係大學<br />\n<br />\n好多文宣都俾人撕咗<br />\n<br />\n而近期成個運動亦都失焦同淡化<br />\n<br />\n連戴口罩日都做唔到<br />\n<br />\n呢個係我嘅推斷<br />\n<br />\n連儂牆雖然無好實質嘅作用<br />\n<br />\n但其實佢將個環境變成我哋抗爭者嘅主場<br />\n<br />\n你諗下啲藍絲行入大埔連儂隧道都要頭dup dup<br />\n<br />\n除此之外 近排嘅文宣工作已經少咗太多<br />\n<br />\n大家諗返最初我哋係點樣眾籌全球登報？<br />\n<br />\n宜家呢一個moment我哋可以行嘅棋唔多<br />\n<br />\n再貿貿然出去打狗 又會好百幾做手足俾狗咬<br />\n<br />\n我哋唔可以再失去任何一個手足<br />\n<br />\n我唔想再睇到有人被自殺<br />\n<br />\n所以我懇請大家 之前文宣嘅 之前勇武嘅 一齊出嚟貼爆個連儂牆佢！<br />\n<br />\n唔係講好咗撕一貼百架咩？<br />\n<br />\n香港係我哋主埸 我要我哋嘅文宣遍地開花<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"accf5d12750ddc18a51400d14c1344df1b9978c8","tid":1644612,"uid":245203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:22:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee60c81d2ccb72022ea594795bd511442da7be01","tid":1644612,"uid":245203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:22:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"20e42dfaaee8851cd5c2d3ff7b2ac0f3b2e8c4b8","tid":1644612,"uid":332797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s